  <brief_title>Safety and Cognitive Function Study of EVP-6124 in Patients With Schizophrenia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Double-Blind Placebo-Controlled 12-Week Phase 2 Study of Two Different Doses of an Alpha-7 Nicotinic Acetylcholine Receptor Agonist(EVP-6124)or Placebo in Schizophrenia Subjects on Chronic Stable Atypical Anti-Psychotic Therapy</official_title>
